      <div class="msgContentFrame">I've been trying to figure out which crafting classes are going to benefit my Lancer the most. It seems that most of my armor is leather based right now, so I'm thinking of going with leatherworking, if for no other reason than to be able to repair my stuff. <br /> <br />But I can't seem to find any information on the types of armor I can wear. At higher levels, can I access heavier armors? Any good suggestions one what crafts (2 tops) would benefit a lancer the most?<div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div>Striveldt <br /> <br /><span style="color:blue">FFXIV: </span> Lancer, Fisher, Culinarian <br /><span style="color:red">FFXI:</span> DRK 55, WAR 30, THF 27, DRG 27 (all retired) <br /><span style="color:yellow">WoW:</span> Hunter 70, Warrior 29, Druid 26, Warlock 22, Shaman 19 (all retired) <br /><span style="color:green">EQII:</span> Shadowknight 36 (retired) <br /></div></div>
