      <div class="msgContentFrame">Fish glue is necessary for the rank 7 or 16 harpoon/spears. You need an alchemist at 10+ to do it or you can buy it for the inflated price it's probably selling for. Some of the rank 20+ armors are crafted by armorers by the way that also has LNC as part of the class list like the Bronze Haubergeon.<div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div><a href="http://lodestone.finalfantasyxiv.com/rc/character/status?cicuid=2639653" title="http://lodestone.finalfantasyxiv.com/rc/character/status?cicuid=2639653" rel="external nofollow">http://lodestone.finalfantasyxiv.com/rc/character/status?cicuid=2639653</a></div></div>
